trans-unit.source: The type of objects in the list.
<c>C</c> must implement the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> interface.
Represents a generic collection of <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> objects that can be individually accessed by index.
trans-unit.target: 인덱스별로 각각 액세스할 수 있는 <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> 개체의 제네릭 컬렉션을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the element to get.
Returns the element at the specified index.
The element at the specified index.
The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.GetItem%2A> method does not remove the element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.GetItem%2A> 메서드는 지정된 된 인덱스에 있는 요소를 제거 하지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: To remove an element from the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 요소를 제거 하는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
-or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />의 반환 값보다 크거나 같은 경우

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> to locate in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" />.
Returns the index of a specific element in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" />.
The index of <paramref name="item" /> if found in the list; otherwise, -1.
trans-unit.target: 목록에 있으면 <paramref name="item" />의 인덱스이고, 그렇지 않으면 -1입니다.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert <c>item</c>.
The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> to insert in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" />.
Inserts an element in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> at the specified index.
After you call <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.Insert%2A>, the elements that follow the insertion point move to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: 호출한 후 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.Insert%2A>, 삽입 지점 다음에 오는 이동 하 여 새 요소로 적용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The indexes of the elements that are moved are also updated.
trans-unit.target: 이동 되는 요소의 인덱스도 업데이트 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: To replace an element at a specified index, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 된 인덱스에 있는 요소를 대체 하려면 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601> is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601> 는 읽기 전용 호출에서 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
-or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />의 반환 값보다 크거나 같은 경우

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> is read-only.
The index of the element to remove.
Removes the element at the specified index.
After you call <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A>, the elements that follow the removed element move to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: 호출한 후 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A>, 제거 된 요소 다음에 오는 이동 하 여 빈된 자리를 채웁니다.

trans-unit.source: The indexes of the elements that are moved are also updated.
trans-unit.target: 이동 되는 요소의 인덱스도 업데이트 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601> is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601> 는 읽기 전용 호출에서 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
-or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />의 반환 값보다 크거나 같은 경우

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> is read-only.
The zero-based index at which to set the element.
The element to set at the specified index.
Replaces the element at the specified index.
The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> method replaces the element at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> 메서드는 지정된 된 인덱스에 요소를 바꿉니다.

trans-unit.source: To add an element to the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.Insert%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 요소를 추가 하는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601>를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601.Insert%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601> is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract%601> 는 읽기 전용 호출에서 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> 메서드.

-or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.ICollectionContract`1.GetCount" />의 반환 값보다 크거나 같은 경우

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> is read-only.
